{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2019/11/26/树莓派Ubuntu重启音频.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"28c12af4-2f88-5bbd-a759-3aaebd2043c7","excerpt":"树莓派Ubuntu重启音频 前一阵子重新拿起来我的树莓派用来放一些学习视频，然而发现ubuntu mate对音频处理有问题，一旦占用结束后有新的应用来占用就会有杂音，感觉ubuntu这个问题出N久了。目前我没找到更好的解决方案，只好重启一下了。","html":"<h1>树莓派Ubuntu重启音频</h1>\n<p>前一阵子重新拿起来我的树莓派用来放一些学习视频，然而发现ubuntu mate对音频处理有问题，一旦占用结束后有新的应用来占用就会有杂音，感觉ubuntu这个问题出N久了。目前我没找到更好的解决方案，只好重启一下了。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token shebang important\">#!/bin/bash</span>\npulseaudio -k <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> alsa force-reload</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2019/11/26/树莓派Ubuntu重启音频.html","date":"November 26, 2019","title":"树莓派Ubuntu重启音频"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2019/11/26/树莓派Ubuntu重启音频.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/movie/2019/11/25/电影补档计划：龙猫.html","title":"电影补档计划：龙猫"},"frontmatter":{"category":"movie"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/movie/2019/11/26/电影补档计划：熔炉.html","title":"电影补档计划：熔炉"},"frontmatter":{"category":"movie"}}}}}